    <item>
      <title>Smartmatic 与 Newsmax 在审判前夕达成诽谤和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/smartmatic-and-newsmax-settle-defamation-case-on-eve-of-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Smartmatic Corp. 已与 Newsmax Media Inc. 达成和解，后者指控这家投票技术公司在 2020 年总统大选期间操纵选举，对唐纳德·特朗普不利。在陪审团审判开始前几天，Smartmatic 终于解决了此案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/smartmatic-and-newsmax-settle-defamation-case-on-eve-of-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 19:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技公司利用与共和党议员的关系来拖延儿童安全法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/kids-online-safety-act-stalled-by-top-house-republican-leaders-big-tech-lobby</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党高层正在推迟具有里程碑意义的美国立法，该立法旨在保护儿童免受网络剥削和欺凌，这暴露了美国共和党内部在社交媒体监管问题上的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/kids-online-safety-act-stalled-by-top-house-republican-leaders-big-tech-lobby</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 19:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷贫困率飙升至 50% 以上，紧缩政策带来沉重打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/poverty-soars-past-50-in-argentina-as-milei-austerity-hits-hard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年上半年，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱推出休克疗法，试图让本已摇摇欲坠的经济重新站起来，该国的贫困率达到了 2001 年金融危机以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/poverty-soars-past-50-in-argentina-as-milei-austerity-hits-hard</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 19:16:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
