    <item>
      <title>纽约市长反对指控，亚当斯的批评者高呼“辞职！”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/eric-adams-corruption-charges-nyc-mayor-defies-calls-for-resignation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，纽约市长官邸格雷西大厦外响起“辞职！”的呼声。这个词被反复重复，淹没了埃里克·亚当斯的声音，他敦促纽约人先听取他的辩护，然后再做出任何判断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/eric-adams-corruption-charges-nyc-mayor-defies-calls-for-resignation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 18:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部调查报告出炉后，超微股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/super-micro-probed-by-us-following-hindenburg-report-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前《华尔街日报》报道称，美国司法部正在根据一份质疑该公司会计做法的做空报告对这家服务器制造商进行调查，此后，该公司股价出现一个月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/super-micro-probed-by-us-following-hindenburg-report-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 15:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国指控纽约市长贪污多年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-mayor-eric-adams-is-indicted-on-bribery-and-fraud-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼哈顿最高联邦检察官在一份严厉的起诉书中声称，纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯多年来持续腐败，收受了外国人超过 10 万美元的巨额贿赂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-mayor-eric-adams-is-indicted-on-bribery-and-fraud-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 14:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯抨击特朗普推动乌克兰与普京谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/biden-to-convene-ukraine-allies-in-germany-surge-military-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯严厉批评唐纳德·特朗普试图向乌克兰施压，以通过谈判结束俄罗斯的战争，并为在选举前继续向基辅提供援助进行辩护，因为冲突已成为政治焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/biden-to-convene-ukraine-allies-in-germany-surge-military-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡访问联合国，从战争走向外交敌对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/israel-s-netanyahu-flies-from-war-to-diplomatic-hostility-with-un-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年前，本雅明·内塔尼亚胡来到联合国，宣扬阿拉伯世界和平的祝福。他回来时，该地区正处于全面战争的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/israel-s-netanyahu-flies-from-war-to-diplomatic-hostility-with-un-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
